    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/8b9531b8c2cd6938db92af04c32a2b33.avif?t=1765757384\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Black Submarine </strong>是一款惊心动魄的水下冒险游戏，让您控制一艘强大的、高科技的潜艇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/814903011ac66a6e85a4610f31f1be74.poster.avif?t=1765757384\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/814903011ac66a6e85a4610f31f1be74.webm?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/814903011ac66a6e85a4610f31f1be74.mp4?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在2086年，太平洋隐藏着深不可测的秘密和难以想象的危机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >航行在危险的水域，面对致命的敌人，并发现海底深处的秘密。该游戏结合了激烈的动作、探索和策略，提供独特的沉浸式体验。  这款游戏融合了紧张刺激的动作、战略探索和战术战斗，带来身临其境且充满挑战的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好潜入这场水下冒险了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特点：</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/ab8b3f071864640830d4783375e89d12.avif?t=1765757384\" width=780 height=154 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单人战役：</strong> 开启一段探索水下世界民间传说故事的旅程。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/17c15f2c409f0fce8352bee5cf6005ff.poster.avif?t=1765757384\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/17c15f2c409f0fce8352bee5cf6005ff.webm?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/17c15f2c409f0fce8352bee5cf6005ff.mp4?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战术战斗：</strong> 使用激光武器和装备来击败危险的海洋生物群。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/9200c5242a708b14b0b1d3965a73a69e.poster.avif?t=1765757384\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/9200c5242a708b14b0b1d3965a73a69e.webm?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/9200c5242a708b14b0b1d3965a73a69e.mp4?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>水下探索：</strong> 在水下洞穴和沉没的海盗船中寻找宝藏和珍贵资源。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/1978a5edea50f48169bf33eaf83002e1.poster.avif?t=1765757384\" width=616 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/1978a5edea50f48169bf33eaf83002e1.webm?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024710/extras/1978a5edea50f48169bf33eaf83002e1.mp4?t=1765757384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潜艇自定义：</strong> 升级您的潜艇，为未来的挑战做好准备。<br> </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >准备潜入吧！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>Black Submarine: deep seek</strong>, 每一次下潜都是充满未知危险的独特冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能否揭开太平洋深渊中埋藏的隐秘真相？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立即潜入，解开静待探索的谜团！</p>",
